data.description: This charming 3 bedroom 2 bathroom gem offers the perfect blend of modern convenience and comfort. The heart of the home has an inviting open floor plan with a fireplace, accented by granite kitchen countertops and fresh paint, creating a style that's perfect for both everyday living and entertaining. The tankless hot water system also ensures endless hot water and energy efficiency. The guest shower features new surround tiling. Outside you'll discover a delightful back patio complete with a pergola for relaxing evenings and a storm shelter for added peace of mind. Conveniently located close to shopping, this home provides easy access to all your daily needs while maintaining a quiet atmosphere. Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful property your new home!
